5000|$|There is some {{controversy}} {{about whether to}} grease carbon <b>seatposts</b> or not. There does not yet {{appear to be a}} consensus. There are now specialty products, referred to as [...] "carbon prep" [...] or [...] "carbon paste", specifically for the interface between carbon and most other materials.|$|R
